On October 15, 2022 at 12:30am after a scary few minutes in triage, a day of painful labor, but just a few quick pushes, our sweet Georgia Autumn Woods made her way into the world and completed our family. Peach, you came to me during a hard time but you’ve been the peace I needed. Your sweet smile, your contagious giggle and your genuine hugs have been some of the best parts of the last year. God really knew exactly what we needed and took his time with you. Mommy, Daddy and your big sisters are so grateful for you ❤️🍑 
It’s so bittersweet to be celebrating my last First Birthday 🥹 but I’m excited to watch you grow and see what you become. 
Happy First Birthday, baby girl. 
#firstbirthday #georgiaautumnwoods #happybirthday
